Name: TorqueL
About the game: TorqueL is a unique 2D 'rolling' & 'extend' platformer/action/puzzle game. Including total 50 chambers, 7 basic routes, and 1 secret route. Interactive music of product version composed by sanodg(Nobuyoshi Sano). Recommended playing with Xbox 360 gamepad. * Win10 + Xbox One Controller problems was fixed on Anniversary Update by pre-install driver renewed.
